{
  "title": "Intricately Crispy Moroccan Black Olives Khlea",
  "description": "Rich and crispy Moroccan dish featuring black olives, perfect for a cozy snack. This low-fat-friendly khlea is made with dashi-extract and served in a bamboo tray.",
